    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total stunner. This beauty is in truly pristine, showroom-ready condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it from day one! It drives like an absolute dream and looks even better in person. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels basically brand new but without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you! Come say hi and see it for yourself!",
