    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This final-run FD3S Spirit R Type A represents the pinnacle of rotary engineering. The 13B-REW power plant maintains exceptional factory-spec compression across both rotors, with the sequential twin-turbocharger system delivering a linear torque curve and seamless transition at 4,500 RPM. The chassis retains its original Bilstein monotube dampers and forged BBS wheels, preserving the legendary 50/50 weight distribution and communicative steering rack. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise five-speed manual and a high-bias Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal power delivery. This is an unmolested, investment-grade example featuring the signature red Recaro carbon-kevlar buckets and pristine factory paint.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
