      "description": "Mint condition. Garage kept. No accidents. Low mileage. Clean title.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, maintained with an obsessive attention to detail that is rarely seen on the secondary market. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like luster, completely free from swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings, having been kept exclusively in a climate-controlled garage and protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Step inside, and you are greeted by a cabin in showroom state; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and matte, showing no signs of bolster wear or creasing, and it still retains that distinct factory-new aroma. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the intricate ambient lighting, functions exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, accompanied by a comprehensive folder of service records documenting every scheduled maintenance interval performed by certified master technicians. It sits on a fresh set of premium tires and delivers a driving experience that is whisper-quiet, tight, and perfectly balanced. This is a meticulously preserved specimen for the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection. Inspection by a specialist is welcomed to verify its flawless state.",
      "price": 44500.0,
