      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of uncompromising standards. This specimen maintains a pristine, showroom-quality aesthetic, reflecting meticulous ownership and exhaustive maintenance. Every surface and mechanical component operates at peak performance, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from its original delivery. An exceptional opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
