      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I am so excited to show you this beauty. It is in absolutely stunning shape\u2014basically brand new! Not a single scratch or speck of dust to be found anywhere. It\u2019s been pampered in a garage since day one and drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019ve been looking for a ride that looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor, this is the one! You\u2019ve gotta see it to believe it! \u2728",
